org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist.impl

Class SoloMusicArtistImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist.impl.MusicArtistImpl
      • org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist.impl.SoloMusicArtistImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.beans.Observable, Artist, MusicArtist, Person, SoloMusicArtist

    public class SoloMusicArtistImpl
extends MusicArtistImpl
implements SoloMusicArtist
    Represents a basic implementation of MusicArtistImpl for a Person, which let the fields to be get and set and furthermore implements the Observable interface which may help to listen to changes of this entity.

    This actually extends MusicArtistImpl since most of the fields of this class are part of MusicArtist and thus shared.
